snippet.title: Automachef - Release Date & Free Demo Trailer! (Nintendo Switch, PC)
snippet.description:
Wishlist & play the free demo on Steam: http://bit.ly/Automachef
Follow Automachef on Twitter: https://twitter.com/automachef

Complicated puzzles, fast food and robots! What else can you ask for? 

On 23rd July get ready to build your automated kitchen empire in Automachef, a challenging kitchen creating puzzler where you'll have full control over each and every machine.

Official website: https://www.automachef.com/
Follow Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17Ltd
Like Team17 on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/

About Team17 Digital Ltd
Founded in 1990, Team17 Digital Limited is a leading international games label that hosts the Worms franchise, Aven Colony, The Escapists, Genesis Alpha One, Overcooked, Sword Legacy: Omen, Yoku’s Island Express, Yooka-Laylee and many more from developers around the world. Visit www.team17.com for more info. 
bit.ly/SubTeam17
